{"tid":2319302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇：麗晶花園情況與當年淘大花園相似 消息指政府正考慮撤離6座部份住戶","createTime":"2020-12-10T04:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T09:35:16.000Z","uid":212626,"like":82,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"60b6d73b5ee4440d214f5e29162676cf6881c424","tid":2319302,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:12:34.000Z","msg":"九龍灣麗晶花園第6座累計有7宗確診。港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇和衛生防護中心總監黃加慶，上午到麗晶花園6座視察，有工作人員到2樓單位拍照和檢查喉管。 約20名身穿全套防護裝備的警員，上午亦進入麗晶花園第6座，上樓記錄住戶資料，現場消息指，衛生署正考慮撤離6座部份住戶。衛生防護中心昨日宣佈，上月17日至今在麗晶花園第6座逗留超過2小時的人，需要強制檢測。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2370065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2370065&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpjcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=6d006d15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2370065</a>"},{"pid":"3f9b14a947e709471e9132a0d12efdd5f91fd0aa","tid":2319302,"uid":241239,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916f07e5461eed7c33a51d772fce02bcf7977083","tid":2319302,"uid":365024,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:12:59.000Z","msg":"君君 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0060bf0e42d58fa17f57c61c1abd2a88dc87b054","tid":2319302,"uid":60279,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"賣樓啦快D 38萬等接貨"},{"pid":"308c4babde604333a2187eae58544f88506aa9d8","tid":2319302,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87e2a788512debf5b4a49aea99c0773bad950d2","tid":2319302,"uid":76804,"like":104,"dislike":5,"score":99,"citedBy